ery strong spines on inner surface; two of these in basal half and third approximately at or just distal to midpoint of tibia. Forewings (Fig. 44 ) extending beyond tip of abdomen; grayish, enfuscated, somewhat darkened at base, especially in anal cell area (nomenclature follows
